<section class=3D"cbm_content  bgnd-grey section-4">
<div class=3D"   section-top-64px section-bottom-64px">
    <div class=3D" container  ">
        <div class=3D" row  mx-auto col-sm-8">

       =20

               =20
                        <div class=3D" col">
                            <div class=3D"copy">
                                <h2 id=3D"card_4-0">
		=09
			Who is <span>CBM Global?</span>
		=09

			</h2>
                                <p>CBM Global Disability Inclusion works al=
ongside and is accountable to people with disabilities in the world=E2=80=
=99s poorest places. We draw on more than <a href=3D"https://cbmg.wpengine.=
com/about-us/who-we-are/our-history">115 years=E2=80=99 experience</a> to f=
ight poverty and exclusion and transform lives. We work with the most margi=
nalised in society to:</p>
<ul>
<li><i aria-hidden=3D"true"></i>Break the cycle of poverty and disability.<=
/li>
<li><i aria-hidden=3D"true"></i>Treat and prevent conditions that lead to d=
isability.</li>
<li><i aria-hidden=3D"true"></i>Build inclusive communities where everyone =
can enjoy their human rights and achieve their full potential.</li>
</ul>
<p>Our approach does not just look to bring about change and transformation=
 at an individual level but we challenge systemic exclusion and discriminat=
ion faced by people with disabilities; a stark reality that the COVID-19 pa=
ndemic has exposed.&nbsp;</p>
<p>We maximise our impact by delivering a combination of inclusive communit=
y-based programmes, advocacy for national and global policy change and incl=
usion advice to other organisations.&nbsp;</p>

                            </div>
                           =20
									<div class=3D"cbm_btn    cbm_btn--multi  ">
											<a class=3D"btn__primary" href=3D"https://cbm-global.org/what-we=
-do" aria-describedby=3D"card_4-0">
												What we do =20
											</a>
										=09
									</div>
                        </div>
                       =20
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
