dle  reorder2">
                          <div class=3D"mb-4 copy ">
              <h2 id=3D"title-5">
		=09
			<span>World-leading expertise</span>
		=09

			</h2>
              <p>Our work and world-leading expertise is focused on four co=
re areas:</p>
<ul>
<li><i aria-hidden=3D"true"></i><a href=3D"https://cbmg.wpengine.com/what-w=
e-do/community-based-inclusive-development">Community based inclusive devel=
opment</a></li>
<li><i aria-hidden=3D"true"></i><a href=3D"https://cbmg.wpengine.com/what-w=
e-do/humanitarian-action">Humanitarian action</a></li>
<li><i aria-hidden=3D"true"></i><a href=3D"https://cbmg.wpengine.com/what-w=
e-do/inclusive-eye-health">Inclusive eye health and neglected tropical dise=
ases</a></li>
<li><i aria-hidden=3D"true"></i><a href=3D"https://cbmg.wpengine.com/what-w=
e-do/community-mental-health">Community mental health</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p>Our programmes in Africa, Asia and Latin America are developed and deliv=
ered with local partner organisations to ensure long-term transformation an=
d accountability in the communities we serve. We draw on learning and evide=
nce from our community work to inform our <a href=3D"https://cbmg.wpengine.=
com/about-us/how-we-work/advocacy">advocacy</a> and achieve systemic change=
 for people with disabilities. We share our expertise, advising governments=
, UN bodies and others on how to ensure inclusion in their own organisation=
s, policies and programmes through our <a href=3D"https://cbm-global.org/in=
clusion-advisory-group" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener">Inclusion Adviso=
ry Group</a>.</p>
<p>We always consider the <a href=3D"https://cbmg.wpengine.com/about-us#gen=
der-disability">intersection of gender and disability</a> in our strategies=
, programmes, advisory and advocacy work.</p>
